headline: Bio-Techne (TECH): Valuation Spotlight Following Expanded Oxford Nanopore Partnership and Growth Strategy Realignment
summary: Bio-Techne (TECH) made headlines by announcing an expanded partnership with Oxford Nanopore Technologies. This move extends their collaboration through 2032 and empowers Bio-Techne to broaden its portfolio of genetic testing products. See our latest analysis for Bio-Techne. Bio-Techne’s partnership expansion with Oxford Nanopore follows a string of innovation-focused announcements, including new advances in spatial biology tools and diagnostic platforms.
